45 documents part of the timeshare trustee foreclosure procedure against timeshares of different
46 owners if both of the following criteria are met:
47 (1) All timeshares are part of the same timeshare project.
48 (2) The declaration giving rise to the right of the managing entity to collect
49 assessments creates default and remedy obligations that are substantially the
50 same for each owner named in the timeshare trustee foreclosure proceeding.
